Add `opentelemetry-instrumentation-writer`, instrumenting the `writerai`
Python SDK chat (`chat.chat` sync/async, streaming and non-streaming) and text
completions (`completions.create` sync/async), emitting standard GenAI semantic
conventions (`gen_ai.*`) via `opentelemetry-util-genai`. Requires
`OTEL_SEMCONV_STABILITY_OPT_IN=gen_ai_latest_experimental`.
